# Vineyard Cron

The Cron library provides functionality for long-running, repetitive Node.js services.

## Example Usage

    (placeholder code)
    const tasks = [ { 'A function', aFunction() }, { 'Another function', anotherFunction() } ]
    const cron = new Cron({tasks, 50000})
    cron.start()
    cron.forceUpdate()
    cron.stop()

